title: GTNH服务端崩溃求大佬谢谢了
author: Bilibili_Hb1
txt_content:

replies.author: 阿狸哥哥
replies.txt_content: Errors like "[FML]: Unable to lookup ..." are NOT the cause of this crash. You can safely ignore these errors. And update forge while you're at it.
